Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.87,0:01:36.24,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Correct, I have already arranged\Nit with the committee.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.24,0:01:40.52,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,The cargo left from Sasebo Port\Nyesterday, and is now making its\Nway here across the Pacific Ocean.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.28,0:01:46.89,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,A MIG-55 D transport helicopter!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.89,0:01:50.56,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’d never have believed I’d get a\Nchance to fly in one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.56,0:01:54.33,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Thank God I have a buddy\Nlike you, Shinji!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.39,0:01:58.93,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well, I thought you guys would be\Ngetting sick of being cramped up\Nin the mountains...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.93,0:02:02.07,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,...so I just invited you on a date!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.07,0:02:06.24,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What?!  Today is really a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.24,0:02:10.88,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I bought this cap for today, Misato!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.88,0:02:12.78,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Where are we headed?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.78,0:02:15.92,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,We’ll take a little jaunt across the\NPacific with a gorgeous cruiser.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.72,0:02:20.74,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Wow!!  One, two, three, four, five...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.74,0:02:22.89,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,...aircraft carriers and four battleships!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.89,0:02:25.82,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Whatta fleet!  I am absolutely sure\Nthe best thing in life is having\Na great buddy!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.82,0:02:27.96,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,That’s your “gorgeous cruiser”?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.96,0:02:29.39,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yeah, she sure is gorgeous!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.39,0:02:33.47,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,That’s the pride of the UN,\Nthe glorious regular carrier\N“Over the Rainbow”!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.47,0:02:34.90,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s huge.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.90,0:02:37.97,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m surprised that such a relic\Nis still afloat.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.97,0:02:39.34,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Naw, it’s not so bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.34,0:02:42.28,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s a vintage model from just before\Nthe Second Impact.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.41,0:02:46.04,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Damn, give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.04,0:02:50.05,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,That ruffian’s gone and brought the\Nsocket for the kid’s toy, so the little\Ngophers can run amuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.79,0:03:02.13,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Ohh!!  Cool!  Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.13,0:03:03.40,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Cool!  Incredible!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.40,0:03:05.46,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Cool!  Mega-cool!  Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.46,0:03:06.57,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,This is way too cool!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.57,0:03:09.74,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,This kind of thing brings a tear\Nto the heart of a real man!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.00,0:03:14.54,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Cool!  Awesome!  Neat!  Wow!  Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.54,0:03:16.81,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,No!  Hey, wait!  Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.71,0:03:23.68,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.68,0:03:25.56,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Stop!  Stop, now!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.62,0:03:31.32,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hello, Misato.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.32,0:03:33.63,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,How have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.63,0:03:36.60,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Fine, how ‘bout you?  You’ve grown\Nsome, haven’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.60,0:03:37.26,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,And how!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.26,0:03:40.97,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m not just taller, my figure’s\Nfilled out as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.97,0:03:42.33,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Let me introduce you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.33,0:03:46.71,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,This is the designated pilot of\NEvangelion Unit 02, the Second Child...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.71,0:03:48.71,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,...Asuka Langley Soryu.
Dialogue: 1,0:03:51.04,0:03:53.42,Background,,0,0,0,Video Text,{\1c&H000000&\p1}m 0 0 l 720 0 720 540 0 540
Dialogue: 2,0:03:51.19,0:03:53.42,Episode (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Video Text,{\blur0.7}{\pos(320,230)}Episode 8:
Dialogue: 3,0:03:51.69,0:03:53.42,Title (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Video Text,{\blur0.7}{\pos(172.444,257)}ASUKA
Dialogue: 4,0:03:52.19,0:03:53.42,Title (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Video Text,{\blur0.7}{\pos(432.889,257)}STRIKES!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.55,0:03:55.05,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What did you do that for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.98,0:03:59.45,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,That’s the viewing fee.  Quite a\Nbargain, don’t you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.45,0:04:03.09,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What?  You think it’s worth that?!\NHere, take a look at mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.09,0:04:06.59,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You insolent dork!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.23,0:04:11.70,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,So, which one is the famous\NThird Child?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.70,0:04:13.60,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Don’t tell me it’s him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:16.74,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Don’t worry, it’s him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.74,0:04:19.94,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well, he looks kinda dull.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.94,0:04:24.54,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I thought you were the leader of this\Ngang of boy scouts...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.54,0:04:27.95,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,...but I was obviously mistaken.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.95,0:04:31.25,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Thank you for your\Nunderstanding, Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.25,0:04:37.19,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Oh, no, thank you for giving me the\Nopportunity to baby-sit even more kids\Nafter such a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.19,0:04:41.79,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well, thank you for your assistance\Nin the marine transport of Eva Unit 02.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.79,0:04:44.96,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Here are the specifications for the\Nemergency power supply socket.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.10,0:04:51.14,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,In the first place, I’d never approve any\Nrequest to activate that toy while at sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.14,0:04:55.74,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Why don’t you just think of it as being\Nprepared for an emergency?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.74,0:05:00.95,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,That’s why the Pacific Fleet\Nis guarding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.95,0:05:05.22,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,When did the UN transform us\Ninto a bloody cargo service?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.22,0:05:09.19,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,If my memory serves me correctly,\Nit was just after a certain\Norganization was established.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.19,0:05:14.63,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Guarding a toy!  What a ridiculously\Ngrandiose assignment for the entire\Nline of the Pacific Fleet!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.63,0:05:18.33,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s still not enough, not when you\Nconsider the importance of the Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.33,0:05:20.13,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Would you sign this document?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.13,0:05:26.40,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Not yet, Eva Unit 02 and its pilot have\Nbeen entrusted to us by the Third\NBranch in Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.40,0:05:28.64,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I won’t let you just waltz in and do\Nas you please!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.64,0:05:30.51,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Then when will you transfer them to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.51,0:05:33.31,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Once we’ve unloaded\Nin New Yokosuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.31,0:05:36.05,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,The ocean is our jurisdiction.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.05,0:05:37.98,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You will follow our orders here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.98,0:05:39.62,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.62,0:05:45.36,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,However, I should remind you that, in\Nthe case of an emergency, our, NERV’s,\Nauthority overrides yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.36,0:05:47.03,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,She’s cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.03,0:05:48.56,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,She looks like Ritsuko...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.56,0:05:51.13,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well, you’re as gallant as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.13,0:05:52.33,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Kaji!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.60,0:05:57.77,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Mr. Kaji, I must insist that you not invite\Nyourself to the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.77,0:05:59.21,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.21,0:06:00.64,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well, excuse us.  Transport us to\NNew Yokosuka, as ordered.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.64,0:06:02.84,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,{\c&HFFFFFF&}This is a date?\N{\c&H00E3FE&}Well, excuse us.  Transport us to\NNew Yokosuka, as ordered.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.84,0:06:04.61,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Cool!  This is just cool!\N{\c&H00E3FE&}Well, excuse us.  Transport us to\NNew Yokosuka, as ordered.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.61,0:06:08.31,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I can’t take anymore!  Those kids are\Nreally going to save the Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.31,0:06:10.48,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,The times have changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.48,0:06:13.72,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I understand that Congress has pinned\Nits hopes on that robot as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.72,0:06:17.32,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,On that toy?  Idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.32,0:06:20.89,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,If they’ve got money to blow on that,\Nthey ought to give a little more to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.50,0:06:28.40,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What are you doing here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.40,0:06:30.04,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Accompanying her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.04,0:06:31.95,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m on a business trip from Germany.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.95,0:06:33.86,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Man, was I careless.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.86,0:06:36.64,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I should have anticipated this.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.64,0:06:38.51,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hey!  Don’t touch me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.51,0:06:40.01,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I can’t help it!
