Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.77,0:07:01.83,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Blue Text,{\fs26}{\c&HFFFF00&}You’re the air conditioner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.83,0:07:02.93,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Blue Text,Wha... wha...\N{\fs26}{\c&HFFFF00&}You’re the air conditioner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.93,0:07:03.94,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Blue Text,Wha... wha...\N{\fs26}{\c&HFFFF00&}You’re so stupid, venting your heat externally.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.94,0:07:05.64,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Blue Text,What are you implying?!!\N{\fs26}{\c&HFFFF00&}You’re so stupid, venting your heat externally.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.64,0:07:05.74,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Blue Text,What are you implying?!!\N{\fs26}{\c&HFFFF00&}The more heat you vent, the colder my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.74,0:07:06.77,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Blue Text,{\fs26}{\c&HFFFF00&}The more heat you vent, the colder my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.77,0:07:07.64,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Blue Text,So, she hasn’t changed,\NMister Shinji Ikari?\N{\fs26}{\c&HFFFF00&}The more heat you vent, the colder my heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.64,0:07:09.34,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Blue Text,So, she hasn’t changed,\NMister Shinji Ikari?\N{\fs26}{\c&HFFFF00&}Then, let us warm your frozen body together!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.34,0:07:10.78,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Blue Text,Um, well...\N{\fs26}{\c&HFFFF00&}Then, let us warm your frozen body together!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.78,0:07:10.91,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Blue Text,Um, well...\N{\fs26}{\c&HFFFF00&}I’m sorry, you can’t light my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.91,0:07:13.38,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Blue Text,How do you know my name?\N{\fs26}{\c&HFFFF00&}I’m sorry, you can’t light my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.38,0:07:13.95,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Blue Text,Well, I ought to know you.\N{\fs26}{\c&HFFFF00&}I’m sorry, you can’t light my heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.95,0:07:14.91,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Blue Text,Well, I ought to know you.\N{\fs26}{\c&HFFFF00&}...put logs on my fire and stoke me with oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.91,0:07:16.75,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Blue Text,You’re pretty famous in our business.\N{\fs26}{\c&HFFFF00&}...put logs on my fire and stoke me with oil.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.75,0:07:17.72,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Blue Text,You’re pretty famous in our business.\N{\fs26}{\c&HFFFF00&}Who is it?  It can’t be.  Is it that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.72,0:07:21.32,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Blue Text,The famous Third Child, who piloted an\NEva in his first battle with no training.\N{\fs26}{\c&HFFFF00&}Who is it?  It can’t be.  Is it that guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.32,0:07:21.59,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Blue Text,The famous Third Child, who piloted an\NEva in his first battle with no training.\N{\fs26}{\c&HFFFF00&}No, it’s this puppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.59,0:07:22.29,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Blue Text,{\fs26}{\c&HFFFF00&}No, it’s this puppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.29,0:07:23.56,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Blue Text,It was just luck.\N{\fs26}{\c&HFFFF00&}No, it’s this puppy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.56,0:07:25.26,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Blue Text,It was just luck.\N{\fs26}{\c&HFFFF00&}You’re telling me that I lost to this puppy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.26,0:07:27.99,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Blue Text,Luck is a part of your destiny,\Nit’s your talent.\N{\fs26}{\c&HFFFF00&}You’re telling me that I lost to this puppy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.99,0:07:28.93,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Blue Text,Luck is a part of your destiny,\Nit’s your talent.\N{\fs26}{\c&HFFFF00&}Yes, he’s a good boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.93,0:07:29.63,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Blue Text,{\c&HFFFF00&}{\fs26}Yes, he’s a good boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.63,0:07:31.16,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Blue Text,Well, I’ll see you later.\N{\fs26}{\c&HFFFF00&}...and he’s faithful, unlike some people!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.16,0:07:31.80,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Blue Text,See ya.\N{\fs26}{\c&HFFFF00&}...and he’s faithful, unlike some people!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.80,0:07:33.54,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,This has got to be a bad joke.\NNo, a nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.53,0:07:38.70,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,So, what do you think about\NMister Shinji Ikari?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.70,0:07:43.38,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,He’s boring.  That’s the great Third\NChild?  What a disappointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.38,0:07:48.08,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,And yet, his synchronization ratio\Nwas well over 40% in combat,\Nwith no prior training.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.08,0:07:49.68,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,That can’t be true!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.68,0:07:52.48,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,That captain’s attitude\Ngets on my nerves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.48,0:07:54.49,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,He’s got a lot of pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.49,0:07:57.16,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Too much pride’s bound to make\Nhim cynical about us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.16,0:08:00.53,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,That Mr. Kaji is pretty... um, lively.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.53,0:08:03.03,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,He hasn’t changed at all, that jerk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.03,0:08:04.44,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hey, Third Child!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.80,0:08:07.14,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.21,0:08:18.74,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Red?  I didn’t know that\NUnit 02 was red.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.74,0:08:21.98,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,The color isn’t the only difference.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.98,0:08:27.15,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,After all, Units 00 and 01 were created\Nas part of a developing process,\Nprototype and test type respectively.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.15,0:08:32.09,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,The fact that it synchronized with an\Nuntrained pilot like you is proof of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.09,0:08:34.53,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,However, Unit 02 is a little different.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.53,0:08:39.86,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Created for actual combat conditions,\Nthis is the world’s first true Evangelion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.86,0:08:41.36,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,This is the final model!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.77,0:08:45.17,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,W... what’s that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.17,0:08:47.84,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,An undersea shock wave!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.84,0:08:49.28,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Something exploded nearby!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.04,0:08:52.11,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What’s that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.01,0:08:57.58,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Is that... an Angel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.58,0:08:59.46,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Is that a real one?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.35,0:09:04.63,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Oh, my gosh.  We’ve got to go back\Nand find Misato...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.79,0:09:08.17,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,This is my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.63,0:09:16.94,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,All ships maintain formation\Nand take evasive action!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.94,0:09:18.54,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Status report!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.54,0:09:22.74,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,The Cymbeline’s gone silent.  The Titus\NAndronicus can’t locate the target!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.74,0:09:25.48,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Damn it!  What in the hell is\Ngoing on here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.48,0:09:26.95,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hello, NERV delivery.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.95,0:09:30.82,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Would you like to order information on\Nthis enemy and countermeasures\Nto use against it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.82,0:09:34.02,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,This is a combat situation!  No\Nunauthorized personnel allowed!!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.02,0:09:37.69,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,This is just my opinion, but I’d say this\Nmust be an Angel attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.69,0:09:39.69,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,All ships, fire at will!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.69,0:09:40.69,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.40,0:09:55.07,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,An AT Field can’t be penetrated with\Nthis kind of firepower.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.07,0:09:57.88,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,But why is an Angel here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.88,0:09:59.25,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,My God, is it after Unit 02?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.65,0:10:04.35,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Where are you taking me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.38,0:10:09.22,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Just wait there a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.22,0:10:10.70,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I can’t believe this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.96,0:10:19.46,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Don’t peep, you pervert!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.46,0:10:20.47,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,{\c&HFFFFFF&}Sorry!\N{\c&H00E3FE&}Don’t peep, you pervert!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.47,0:10:21.40,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Don’t peep, you pervert!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.40,0:10:24.40,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Why are all boys such perverted jerks?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.11,0:10:33.85,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Here we go, Asuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.99,0:10:42.25,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Why won’t it sink?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.25,0:10:44.66,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I knew it... only an Eva can beat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.66,0:10:53.00,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Let’s go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.00,0:10:55.50,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.67,0:11:01.27,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hey, what are these\Nentry plug suits for?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.27,0:11:02.61,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Are you dense?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.61,0:11:05.78,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,We’re going to beat it with my Unit 02!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.28,0:11:10.28,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,No way.  Do you have an\Napproval from Misato?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.28,0:11:12.23,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’ll get permission after I’ve beaten it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.02,0:11:19.86,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Now, I’ll show you how magnificent\Nmy piloting is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.86,0:11:21.96,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Just don’t disturb me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.27,0:11:30.21,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,This is odd.  It seems to be\Nlooking for something.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.24,0:11:33.44,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I didn’t expect to see an Angel here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.44,0:11:35.34,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,This isn’t how it’s supposed to be, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.34,0:11:37.31,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,That is what Unit 02 is for...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.31,0:11:39.58,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,...and I’ve generously provided a\Nsecond pilot as a reserve.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.61,0:11:45.12,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,If worst comes to worst, you can\Nescape by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.12,0:11:46.18,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I know.
