Dialogue: 2,0:11:53.48,0:11:56.27,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Blue Text,{\c&HFFFF00&}Anfang des Nervenanschlusses!\N{\c&H00E3FE&}Beginning nerve link-up!
