Dialogue: 2,0:11:56.27,0:11:59.23,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Blue Text,{\c&HFFFF00&}Ausulsses vonlinks-kleigung!\N{\c&H00E3FE&}Nerve link-up commencing!
Dialogue: 1,0:11:59.23,0:12:01.03,Background,,0,0,0,Video Text,{\blur3}{\bord0\shad0\1c&H09115A&\an5\pos(320,420)\p1m 0 0 l 268 0 268 38 0 38}
Dialogue: 2,0:11:59.23,0:12:01.03,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Blue Text,{\c&HFFFF00&}Synchro-start!\N{\c&H00E3FE&}Synchronization start!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.90,0:12:06.77,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Program error?  What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.77,0:12:09.77,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Thought noise!  I told you not\Nto disturb me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.77,0:12:10.81,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.81,0:12:15.18,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You’re thinking in Japanese aren’t\Nyou?  Think in German.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.18,0:12:18.99,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Oh, okay... strudel...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.99,0:12:19.78,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.78,0:12:24.29,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Fine, stop trying.  Switch the\Nlanguage to basic Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.26,0:12:30.53,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Evangelion Unit 02, activate.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.53,0:12:33.50,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Telex from the Othello!  Eva Unit 02\Nis in the process of activation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.50,0:12:34.57,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What the...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.57,0:12:35.91,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Nice going, Asuka!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.50,0:12:42.01,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,No!  Abort the activation\Nsequence!  Reset it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.01,0:12:44.04,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I don’t care!  Asuka!  Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.04,0:12:46.81,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!  Eva and its\Npilot are under our control!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.81,0:12:49.41,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You’re violating my command authority!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.41,0:12:53.28,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?  This is\Nan emergency!  Who gives a damn\Nabout your procedures?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.28,0:12:54.12,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,{\c&HFFFFFF&}You and your procedures!!\N\N\N\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.12,0:12:55.75,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,White Text,{\c&HFFFFFF&}You and your procedures!!\N{\c&H00E3FE&}You’re not serious?  You do know that\NUnit 02 is still using the B equipment?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:58.56,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You’re not serious?  You do know that\NUnit 02 is still using the B equipment?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.56,0:13:00.96,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,If we fall in the sea, we’re done for!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.96,0:13:02.56,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,And if we don’t, we’ll be fine, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.56,0:13:04.20,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Shinji, are you in there too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.20,0:13:05.00,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.00,0:13:06.50,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Kids!  Two kids!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.50,0:13:08.33,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,This is a good opportunity...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.33,0:13:09.71,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Asuka, launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.20,0:13:13.14,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.14,0:13:14.64,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.61,0:13:22.48,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.48,0:13:23.75,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,That way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.75,0:13:26.35,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,We’ve only got 58 seconds left!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.35,0:13:28.15,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I am well aware of that!  Misato!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.15,0:13:31.59,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Get the external power supply\Nsocket onto the flight deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.59,0:13:32.59,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’ve got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.59,0:13:33.93,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What is she going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.93,0:13:35.53,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Here we go!  Jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.53,0:13:37.03,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Jump?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.06,0:13:41.56,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.55,0:13:55.98,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,The power socket is in place!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:57.92,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Reactor connection completed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.92,0:14:01.25,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,The deck is ready for Eva landing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.25,0:14:03.25,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,All hands, prepare for impact!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.25,0:14:04.09,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I can’t believe this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.09,0:14:06.56,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Eva 02, landing on deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.73,0:14:18.20,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,No!  Whatta waste...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.20,0:14:20.87,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Target is approaching rapidly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.87,0:14:22.87,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s coming!  9 o’clock!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.87,0:14:24.58,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Switching to external power!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.11,0:14:29.52,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Switch completed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.82,0:14:32.05,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,But we don’t have any weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.05,0:14:33.62,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,The progressive knife should\Nbe good enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.46,0:14:43.76,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s bigger than I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.76,0:14:45.03,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,That’s what I figured!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.37,0:14:48.77,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What are they going to do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.77,0:14:51.54,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hand-to-hand combat is the best\Nway to defeat Angels.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.62,0:15:06.12,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Good work, Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.12,0:15:09.25,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,This isn’t a game!  Look at the mess\Nyou’ve made of the deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.43,0:15:18.00,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,See?!  It’s sinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.00,0:15:18.86,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.86,0:15:21.80,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s impossible to fight underwater\Nwith the B equipment!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.80,0:15:23.37,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You never know...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.37,0:15:24.64,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,...till you try!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.19,0:15:45.09,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What a waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.09,0:15:46.40,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,How much cable is left?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.66,0:15:49.29,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,1,200 meters more!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.29,0:15:50.86,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.86,0:15:52.86,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,We can deal with it... somehow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.86,0:15:54.27,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’ve got to do something...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.27,0:16:00.91,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,The cable’s going to run out!\NBrace for the shock!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.84,0:16:07.81,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.81,0:16:09.61,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Eva missed the target!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.61,0:16:12.42,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’ve got to change the disk.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.42,0:16:15.29,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,My God!  A Yak-38 Custom!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.29,0:16:17.22,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hey, Katsuragi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.22,0:16:19.06,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Kaji!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.06,0:16:21.80,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’ve got something to deliver,\Nso I’ll be taking off now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.79,0:16:25.56,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.56,0:16:28.30,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Take care of the rest of this,\NCaptain Katsuragi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.30,0:16:32.10,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,H... he ran away.  I don’t believe it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.10,0:16:34.31,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,The target is approaching Eva again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.34,0:16:36.97,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s coming again!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.97,0:16:38.68,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’ll finish it off this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.48,0:16:44.68,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What?!  It’s not working!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.68,0:16:46.22,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,That’s because this is B type equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.22,0:16:47.89,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What’re you gonna do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.89,0:16:48.92,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What am I gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.92,0:16:51.99,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You’re the Third Child,\Naren’t you?  Do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.99,0:16:52.80,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Here it comes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.50,0:16:59.10,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,A m...m...mouth?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.10,0:17:00.57,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,That’s because it’s an Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.27,0:17:06.07,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Eva 02 has entered the target’s body.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.07,0:17:07.98,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Does that mean that the\NEva’s been eaten?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.21,0:17:12.44,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,This is like fishing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.44,0:17:14.82,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Fishing?  Yes, fishing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.15,0:17:19.02,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,From a bad situation to a worse one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.02,0:17:20.26,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hey, get off me already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.25,0:17:23.59,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hey, get off me already, you pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.59,0:17:25.59,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,But we’ve got to free ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.59,0:17:27.09,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Asuka, do you read me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.09,0:17:28.76,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Don’t let go of it!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.33,0:17:31.26,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Captain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.26,0:17:32.46,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.46,0:17:34.46,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m requesting your cooperation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.27,0:17:39.67,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,A point-blank assault by the\Ntwo surviving battleships?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.67,0:17:40.64,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.64,0:17:46.54,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,We’ll sink two of the evacuated\Nbattleships on top of the umbilical\Ncable to set a trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.54,0:17:50.21,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,When the Eva opens the target’s mouth,\Nboth ships will rush into the opening.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.21,0:17:57.96,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,They will fire all of their bow turret\Ncannons and then self-destruct,\Ndestroying the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.96,0:17:59.46,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,That’s absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.46,0:18:03.73,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Absurd, perhaps, but not impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.73,0:18:04.73,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.73,0:18:08.67,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,All hands abandon ship!  Repeat,\Nall hands, abandon ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.67,0:18:12.00,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,The frigates will rescue the lifeboats!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.00,0:18:13.97,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,But what about the Eva?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.97,0:18:16.51,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Not to worry.  They’ll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.51,0:18:20.65,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hey!  Don’t use Unit 02\Nwithout my permission!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.65,0:18:23.28,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Do the two of you understand\Nthe operation?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.28,0:18:24.72,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’ll do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.72,0:18:25.85,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.15,0:18:33.36,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,All ships, open the Kingston valve!\NScuttle at point z.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.36,0:18:34.46,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.46,0:18:35.63,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Cable reverse!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.40,0:18:44.60,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Eva has started to surface!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.60,0:18:46.38,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,T-minus 70 to contact!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.17,0:18:51.38,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hey, you’re touching my... get off!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.38,0:18:54.72,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,But we’ve got to open its mouth\Nor we’ll be killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.38,0:19:00.08,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,T-minus 60 to contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.08,0:19:00.99,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Status on the Angel’s mouth?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.99,0:19:02.12,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s still not open!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.59,0:19:07.66,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Both battleships are sinking\Ntowards the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.66,0:19:10.19,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Eva is continuing to\Nsurface, T-minus 50 to contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.19,0:19:11.13,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,No, it won’t open!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.13,0:19:12.30,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,No time left!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.44,0:19:21.64,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Target has passed beneath the Tempest!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.64,0:19:23.61,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hurry!!  Or you won’t make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.61,0:19:25.44,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Don’t get any strange ideas.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.44,0:19:26.28,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.28,0:19:28.78,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Anyway, just concentrate\Non your thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.78,0:19:29.78,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You can say that again!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.02,0:19:36.69,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,T-minus 20 to contact!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.46,0:19:41.59,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,T-minus 15 to contact!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.59,0:19:43.72,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Fade In & Out,{\fad(170,170)}Open!  Open!  Open!  Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.72,0:19:46.10,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Fade In & Out,{\fad(170,170)}Open!  Open!  Open!  Open!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.58,0:19:59.08,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.17,0:20:22.97,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Christ!  That was rather spectacular!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.97,0:20:26.54,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I had to improvise for underwater\Ncombat, I should have anticipated it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.54,0:20:28.81,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s rare for you to regret something.\NIs this some kind of self-analysis?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.81,0:20:32.31,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Cut it out.  We’ve collected a lot\Nof valuable data.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.31,0:20:33.31,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.31,0:20:36.35,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Misato...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.35,0:20:37.85,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,This really is something special.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.92,0:20:46.36,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,P...pair of... look...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.36,0:20:48.49,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I don’t believe this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.49,0:20:51.63,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,They broke their synchronization ratio\Nrecords, didn’t they?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.63,0:20:55.27,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,In only 7 seconds.  It must have\Nbeen due to the danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.27,0:20:57.00,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hey, where’s Kaji?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.00,0:21:00.88,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,He ran off earlier.  That idiot’s got to\Nbe back at headquarters by now!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.27,0:21:05.94,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It was a pretty eventful trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.94,0:21:07.85,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Was it caused by this, I wonder?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.78,0:21:15.42,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s already restored itself this far.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.42,0:21:21.53,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s frozen inside Dura-Bakelite,\Nbut it’s still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.53,0:21:23.56,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,This is the keystone of the Human\NInstrumentality Project, isn’t it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.56,0:21:24.53,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.53,0:21:26.66,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,This is the first human being...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.66,0:21:27.66,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,...Adam.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.90,0:21:33.47,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,She may have looked cute, but she\Nwas a real bitch.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.47,0:21:36.57,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well, we won’t have to see her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.57,0:21:39.18,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yeah, ol’ Mister Big Shot has to\Nsee her at work though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.18,0:21:40.75,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m really feeling sorry for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.56,0:21:57.09,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,My name is Asuka Langley Soryu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.09,0:21:57.80,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m very pleased to meet you.
