Dialogue: 4,0:23:05.80,0:23:08.47,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Video Text,Deploying for large scale\Nshoreline interception...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.47,0:23:16.34,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,...Asuka and Shinji’s first close\Nteamwork results in their being\Nroughed up due to their bad terms.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.34,0:23:20.98,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Misato gets a plan to achieve\Ntheir perfect unison.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.98,0:23:24.88,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,A six-day-long drama for human\Ndestiny shall begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.88,0:23:28.12,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,The next episode:\N“With One Accord in a Flash.”
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.12,0:23:30.93,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well, we’ll make you a bargain!
